PROLIX
---------------

A procedural generation library for 3D terrain environments.

---------------

prolix.heightmap

USAGE- heightmap.create(SIZE, SEED)
SIZE is any integer that's a power of two.
SEED is any integer or word combination.
Returns a type double SIZE x SIZE array

	heightmap.preview(LANDSCAPE)
LANDSCAPE is any type double nxn array where n is a power of two
Creates a grayscale image in the running directory of the heightmap generated.

heightmap uses a diamond-square algorithm to generate a natural looking landscape across a grid. 

